Logs.Text: Recruiter asked if I have any allergies to dinosaur dander or being eaten. I said no. They seemed relieved.

Description: Responsible for the maintenance of electric perimeter fencing (Sector 9). Duties include the daily feeding of "Assets" (high-velocity carnivores), testing tension wires, and ensuring the backup generators do not fail during tropical storms. Must be willing to work night shifts in torrential rain.
Notes: High turnover rate for this position. The last guy "disappeared" into the long grass. Need to ask about health insurance premiums.
